{
  "body": "**Uberon term**\nUBERON:0000379 tracheal mucosa\n- UBERON:0001826 nasal cavity mucosa\n\n**Bug description**\n\nIntuitively, the parent-child relationship from Uberon shown below does not seem correct:\nUBERON:0000379 tracheal mucosa\n- UBERON:0001826 nasal cavity mucosa\n\n[Original issue from HumanDiseaseOntology](https://github.com/DiseaseOntology/HumanDiseaseOntology/issues/1541)",
  "comments": [
    {
      "id": "IC_kwDOAAidd87Pc7AR",
      "author": {
        "login": "dosumis"
      },
      "authorAssociation": "MEMBER",
      "body": "Agreed.  Looks like this comes from inference.\n\n@dragon-ai-agent please fix by changing respiratory airway to trachea in this axiom:\n\nUBERON:0000379 tracheal mucosa\nEquivalent to\n([mucosa](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/ols4/ontologies/uberon/classes/http%253A%252F%252Fpurl.obolibrary.org%252Fobo%252FUBERON_0000344?lang=en) and [part of](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/ols4/ontologies/uberon/properties/http%253A%252F%252Fpurl.obolibrary.org%252Fobo%252FBFO_0000050?lang=en) some [respiratory airway](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/ols4/ontologies/uberon/classes/http%253A%252F%252Fpurl.obolibrary.org%252Fobo%252FUBERON_0001005?lang=en))\n\nIf this doesn't fix, also check for hard coded UBERON:0001826 nasal cavity mucosa subclassOf UBERON:0000379 tracheal mucosa",
